{"tid":1200304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【動畫】8車撞一地屎夾腳司機：唔好睇熱鬧","createTime":"2019-06-10T17:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T17:26:24.000Z","uid":137628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7f9fca7c554c55d4e18e69df930babfe82ad5a","tid":1200304,"uid":137628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:17:24.000Z","msg":"Published on 18 Aug 2016<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大埔吐露港公路昨日在1小時內先後發生兩宗連環撞車意外，共涉及12輛汽車，4人受傷；其中8車相撞中一輛吸糞車被撞穿喉管導致大量糞便液體流出，現場臭氣熏天。消防員到場救人之餘，亦忙開喉沖淡臭味。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VWWAhdvr_o4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVWWAhdvr_o4&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=a5a095cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VWWAhdvr_o4</a><br />\n<br />\n頭先睇YouTube 搵到，真係好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家記得注意路面安全，小心駕駛啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"bc22da4b4665714b59463d7036d6335c65f72f51","tid":1200304,"uid":137628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4c36ef953f1d36f35505c4821f69a8e4143adaf2","tid":1200304,"uid":137628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:22:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f9d0c69e9796dc9c6b413a062c7a28cfbd1c60c0","tid":1200304,"uid":137628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:26:24.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}